OL,3,CMini heatwave set to scorch parts of
OL,4,CLondon after wet start to July
OL,6,FParts of London and the South East the
OL,7,FUK are set to experience a mini
OL,8,Fheatwave with temperatures rising to
OL,9,F30C.
OL,11,FThe hot weather comes after well above-
OL,12,Faverage rainfall figures in the first
OL,13,Fhalf of the month, including a weather
OL,14,Fwarning for rain on Tuesday evening.
OL,16,FHowever, by Friday, temperatures could
OL,17,Freach 30C in the capital before milder
OL,18,Fconditions return on Sunday.
