OL,3,CMini heatwave set to scorch parts of
OL,4,CLondon after wet start to July
OL,6,FMet Office spokesperson Nicola Maxey
OL,7,Fsaid night-time temperatures could
OL,8,Fstay in the low 20s for parts of south-
OL,9,Feast England ` officially classified
OL,10,Fas "tropical nights" if they do not
OL,11,Fdrop below 20C ` with there being
OL,12,Fhealth implications for the elderly or
OL,13,Finfirm.
OL,15,FShe said there was still uncertainty
OL,16,Fover how soon the milder conditions
OL,17,Fwould come in, with the possibility
OL,18,Fthat the South East could retain its
OL,19,Fheat a little longer than elsewhere.
