OL,3,CMini heatwave set to scorch parts of
OL,4,CLondon after wet start to July
OL,6,FMeanwhile, parts of the country have
OL,7,Falready well-exceeded July's average
OL,8,Frainfall figures despite only being
OL,9,Fhalfway through the month.
OL,11,FThe Met Office spokesperson said
OL,12,FEngland had 97% of July's average
OL,13,Frainfall between July 1 and 15, Wales
OL,14,Fhad 65%, Scotland 49% and Northern
OL,15,FIreland 47%.
OL,17,FLondon has had 154% of its July
OL,18,Faverage already and Dorset 120%.
OL,19,FEdinburgh has only had 40% and Dundee
OL,20,F33%.
