OL,3,CMini heatwave set to scorch parts of
OL,4,CLondon after wet start to July
OL,6,FMs Maxey said: "There are quite big
OL,7,Fregional differences but overall it's
OL,8,Flooking like a wet month so far.
OL,10,F"There is a caveat that, with a dry
OL,11,Fcouple of weeks, by the end of the
OL,12,Fmonth things could even themselves
OL,13,Fout."
OL,15,FShe said that two or three heavy
OL,16,Fdownpours often caused much of a
OL,17,Flocation's July rainfall totals,
OL,18,Frather than a prolonged period of wet
OL,19,Fweather.
