OL,6,FSt Swithin's Day on Monday `
OL,7,Ftraditionally said to predict the next
OL,8,F40 days of weather ` was another wet
OL,9,Fone for much of England and Wales.
OL,11,FBut the Met Office said conditions
OL,12,Fnext week would be "changeable" rather
OL,13,Fthan just rainy, with temperatures
OL,14,Fclose to average.
